Titolo: Kingdom Under Fire: Circle of Doom

Anno: 2007

Descrizione: Kingdom Under Fire: Circle of Doom is a 2007 action role-playing game developed by Blueside and published by Microsoft Game Studios for the Xbox 360. It is the fourth installment in the Kingdom Under Fire series. Chronologically the game's story follows Kingdom Under Fire: The Crusaders released in 2004. Unlike the previous Kingdom Under Fire games, Circle of Doom lacks the real-time strategy elements, with much of the gameplay focus being on hack and slash combat.
It was released in Australia on December 5, 2007, in Japan on December 13, 2007, in North America on January 8, 2008, and in Europe on February 1, 2008.

Genere: Non specificato


Valutazione: 55
